column5: I am going up to Nippissing next week and was just wondering if anyone has been out in the Anglers Haven area?  Thats where we are staying and did have success there last year.
I think you should join them guys on this thread NIP G2G  Leechman
Lot's of ice and lot's of snow.  My shack is out on the south shore and has been pretty slow the last little while.
are the ice bungalows out as of yet?
pretty sure all operators have their huts out
Lots were out between Dec. 28th and the 31st. The rest were all out by the 2nd weekend in Jan.
How was it? I didn't have much success at Anglers Haven last year, but am thinking about heading out again in a couple weeks. What's the word?

Was out at the beginning of the year, and caught 15 Eyes ALL UNDER THE SLOT (yes we put some back) caught them with the great people from the Waltonian.  Looks like the fishery is on the comeback I says.
